Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,参ったね　こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前ら　もっと気合入れて漕げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何ださっきから　鳥の声か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい風吹いてきたな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:51.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,驚いたね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,完全に風を操ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　どこから乗り込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:01.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや何　先の港で船頭と取引してね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この強壮剤と引換に乗っけてもらった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,たまにゃあ船旅もいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた　あいつらが見えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:13.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありゃ「とりかぜ」って蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:31.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺ら蟲師はこういう石笛で蟲を誘き寄せたりする事もあるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さん　誰かに教わったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　ただずっと気晴らしに吹いてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつらが応えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃ大したもんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今のが「強く吹け」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「休め」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すげぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どら　こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,微妙に音が違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:37.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それに　群れの意思とあんまり違う事には応えてくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつらにも都合がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,恐れいったね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:47.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかしお前さん　口笛を使うのは昼だけか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:51.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　夜はこいつらも塒に帰るみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夜には決して吹かん事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:57.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:01.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,多分　悪い事が起こる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,土産か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:21.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　でも高そうだし　無理だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そのうち買えるようになるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあな　上手くやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　イブキ　ちょっと来い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　今日は一時どうなるかと思ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:39.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見ろ　他の奴らより早く着いたな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:43.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前もようやく足を引っ張らなくなってきたし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:48.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,正式な水夫として雇うよう　船主にかけあってやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,次の港はお前の里の近くだろう　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く着いたら　里に帰って休んでいいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一人前になったって言ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,喜んでくれるよな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱりいないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しまった　そう言や
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に何も起こらないな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うるせぇぞ　イブキ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昼間のもお前か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　今日のところは大目に見てやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつも浮かれることくらいあんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　起きろ　浸水してるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　この穴は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く穴を塞げ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水を汲み出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,駄目だ　間に合わねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イブキさん　無事だったのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:25.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,船　沈んじまったって聞いたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ　何とか小船で岸まで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも船が沈んじまっちゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今回の賃料はもらえたのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:46.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だこりゃ　どうしてこんなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,質で換金してきてくれるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やれやれ　困ったね　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.65,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,当面　この子らに何かを食べさせればいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あら　何よこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:21.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嫌だ　今朝は何ともなかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何してやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「よう」じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:37.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いやー　お前が売りに来るものは真贋入乱れてるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:43.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当に希少なものはこの奥のほうに仕舞い込んでんだろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういうもんは仕事道具だ　売れやせん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,少し疑い深くなってるな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見るくらいならいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,てめえにゃ目の毒なだけだ　化野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぜっ返すなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんください　先生　いらっしゃいますか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,先生　内の女房を見てやってくだせい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:12.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙な病になって　村の医者にゃ分からないと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙な病？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:48.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この通り　体の色が昨日からどす黒くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どんどん体が冷たく…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　わかるか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「呼蠱」だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:11.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海辺の岩などに穴を開けて棲みつく蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:17.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,穴に風が吹き込む笛のような音で集まり繁殖する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:23.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あまり増えると　体の弱い者には毒となる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:28.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　なぜこんなところに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:36.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういや　倅が帰ってきてから　あちこちに穴が…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしや　息子さん船乗りで？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　乗ってた船は沈んじまったがね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今どこに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:54.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,土産に高価なもんを買ってきたもんで　質屋に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　ギンコ　治療法はあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:06.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とにかく　蟲を遠ざけるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつで家の外へ誘き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺が出て行ったら　家中の穴を土で塞いでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほれ　お前らの塒はここだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だいぶ楽になったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　顔色も良くなってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:08.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　先生　本当にありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:13.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一時はどうなることかと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いえいえ　そんなそんな　礼には及びませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱりお前だったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,言ったろう　悪い事は起こると
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,つい　浮かれてて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もうすんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:57.05,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　あの石笛すげぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.05,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,売らんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは「呼蠱」が開けた穴でなけりゃいかんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その中でも使えるものは少ない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.05,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だからいいんじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,探してきてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,素人にゃ宝の持ち腐れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「呼蠱」が戻ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:33.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:41.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　どこ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:55.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　なぜこんなことをしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:01.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だって　癪じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:05.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺ばかり　こんなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ　お袋さん死んじまうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:16.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの人は　本当の母さんにはなってくれないから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:24.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,船で石笛の話をしたな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:31.79,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつは蟲を本来あるべき場所へ戻すために使う物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:39.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが中には　それ以外の目的に利用した蟲師もいた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうやって利用し続けた者は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆いずれは身を滅ぼした
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,周囲一帯を巻き込んでな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:57.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も　このままお袋さんを亡くせば　戻れなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も言ったじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲には蟲の都合があると
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分の都合でねじ曲げりゃ　報いが生じる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その能力をどう使うかは自分次第だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:24.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,己がどういう者になるのか　自分で選んで決めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,朝を待って　「とりかぜ」を呼べ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:48.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「とりかぜ」が笛に似た声で鳴くのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「呼蠱」があいつらの好物だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつ　言った通りするかね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さぁね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イブキ　何口笛なんぞ吹いてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:32.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母さんが大変な時に　この薄情者が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.64,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,来た
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　竜巻か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やりおったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:03.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その後　その少年を里で見た者はなかったという
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お兄さん　風待ちかい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,寄ってかないかい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　あの船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,またあの船か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体どうやってんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このべた凪の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:56.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さぁなぁ　どえらいカラクリでも積んでのかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,潮わく谷
